1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,853
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:56,144 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 12=

11
00:01:04,359 --> 00:01:06,239
You only dare to throw hidden weapons,

12
00:01:06,560 --> 00:01:08,359
but not to face me in person?

13
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:10,680
My lady heard you're unbeatable, Mr. Su.

14
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:11,840
She sent me

15
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:13,680
to invite you for a chat.

16
00:01:17,239 --> 00:01:18,760
And if I say no?

17
00:01:18,959 --> 00:01:20,159
That's fine.

18
00:01:20,159 --> 00:01:22,079
I happen to know
where Miss Lin Ningxue is.

19
00:01:22,400 --> 00:01:24,480
Don't blame me
if something happens to her.

20
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:33,760
This is...

21
00:01:34,319 --> 00:01:35,439
A dart from the Shan family.

22
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:39,000
Shan Yingying,
what are you up to this time?

23
00:01:53,159 --> 00:01:53,879
Mr. Gu.

24
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:56,840
He's here.

25
00:01:58,959 --> 00:01:59,760
Leave.

26
00:02:00,079 --> 00:02:02,920
Mr. Gu, my reward...

27
00:02:02,959 --> 00:02:03,920
Out.

28
00:02:07,359 --> 00:02:08,280
Bring him in.

29
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,360
Mr. Gu.

30
00:02:43,759 --> 00:02:45,280
Knew it was you all along.

31
00:02:47,759 --> 00:02:49,439
Don't use the martial hall's darts.

32
00:02:57,039 --> 00:02:58,560
What's going on between
you and Jiang Yao?

33
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:00,439
Ningxue's furious.

34
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,360
Isn't it obvious?

35
00:03:03,879 --> 00:03:05,360
It's a setup by Gu Yuanbing.

36
00:03:05,439 --> 00:03:06,719
He lured me there on purpose.

37
00:03:06,919 --> 00:03:07,639
Nothing happened

38
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,319
between me and her.

39
00:03:09,919 --> 00:03:11,360
You expect me to believe that?

40
00:03:12,639 --> 00:03:15,360
You've been hiding right under my nose.

41
00:03:15,639 --> 00:03:16,639
You've got an agenda

42
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:18,159
by getting close to Ningxue.

43
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,719
That's between me and her.

44
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:23,560
I'll explain it myself.

45
00:03:24,039 --> 00:03:25,159
If there's nothing else,

46
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,159
I'm leaving.

47
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,840
I didn't say you could leave.

48
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:36,360
Make your move.

49
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,479
Enough?

50
00:03:42,319 --> 00:03:43,280
I'm just getting started.

51
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:49,719
Too rush.

52
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:50,879
Weak stance.

53
00:03:50,879 --> 00:03:52,360
You're wide open.

54
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:54,080
Cut the crap!

55
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,319
Let me go. That's cheating.

56
00:04:05,919 --> 00:04:06,960
I'm not even trying.

57
00:04:07,439 --> 00:04:08,639
You've got no balance.

58
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:10,759
Who's there?

59
00:04:16,759 --> 00:04:18,040
(Shan Guohao, Shan Family Head)
Coming to challenge the Shan family?

60
00:04:18,199 --> 00:04:19,560
(Shan Guohao, Shan Family Head)
Think we've got no one left?

61
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:22,759
Dad, he's my friend,

62
00:04:22,759 --> 00:04:23,879
not here to challenge us.

63
00:04:24,319 --> 00:04:25,360
Why didn't you say so?

64
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:27,360
I almost hurt him.

65
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:32,439
Dad, you okay?

66
00:04:33,439 --> 00:04:34,560
I'm fine.

67
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,879
This kid is impressive.

68
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,519
Has he reached Mystic-level too?

69
00:04:41,839 --> 00:04:42,519
Mr. Shan.

70
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:46,360
To think someone so young

71
00:04:46,519 --> 00:04:48,439
could fight me to a draw.

72
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:51,560
Looks like Fan City's got
some real talents lately.

73
00:04:51,839 --> 00:04:52,519
Dad,

74
00:04:52,519 --> 00:04:54,560
he's from our martial hall.

75
00:04:54,959 --> 00:04:55,560
What?

76
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:56,959
How come I didn't know

77
00:04:56,959 --> 00:04:58,720
we had someone this good?

78
00:04:58,959 --> 00:04:59,839
What's your name?

79
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,240
Su Wubing!

80
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:15,079
(Head Disciple, Shan Martial Hall)
Mr. Shan, long time no see.

81
00:05:17,079 --> 00:05:17,959
For real?

82
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,560
Absolutely.

83
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:24,199
Everyone in Fan City knows

84
00:05:24,199 --> 00:05:25,879
the Lin and Shan families are close.

85
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:29,279
Shan Yingying must've challenged him

86
00:05:29,519 --> 00:05:32,560
to avenge Lin Ningxue.

87
00:05:33,839 --> 00:05:35,560
This is our chance.

88
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,439
When he crashed the wedding,

89
00:05:37,759 --> 00:05:39,040
the Shan family was in on it too..

90
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:42,240
Still haven't settled that score.

91
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:43,959
Mr. Gu.

92
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,279
Then I'll...

93
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:46,439
Get ready.

94
00:05:46,959 --> 00:05:49,839
After tonight, you'll be head
of the Shan family.

95
00:05:51,079 --> 00:05:52,480
Thank you, Mr. Gu.

96
00:05:54,439 --> 00:05:56,120
Tch. Traitor.

97
00:05:59,839 --> 00:06:03,160
Mr. Shan, know when to back down.

98
00:06:04,279 --> 00:06:06,959
The Shan family can't hold
on much longer.

99
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:09,360
If you side with Mr. Gu,

100
00:06:09,959 --> 00:06:11,560
life will be much better.

101
00:06:12,639 --> 00:06:13,560
Enough talk.

102
00:06:13,639 --> 00:06:14,680
Finish him.

103
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:15,079
Got it.

104
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,959
You think a traitor like him?

105
00:06:19,879 --> 00:06:22,240
Today I'll enforce family law,

106
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:24,079
and expel him from the sect.

107
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,720
Then I'll deal with you.

108
00:06:31,839 --> 00:06:32,360
Dad!

109
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:33,480
Dad!

110
00:06:34,639 --> 00:06:36,279
How did he get this strong?

111
00:06:37,959 --> 00:06:38,439
Guards!

112
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:50,240
I hear you're early Mystic-level.

113
00:06:50,639 --> 00:06:51,759
Take this.

114
00:06:51,759 --> 00:06:53,720
No one can beat you tonight.

115
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:55,319
This... this is...?

116
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:58,279
Our Gu family's latest product.

117
00:06:58,759 --> 00:06:59,879
Only one of its kind.

118
00:07:00,959 --> 00:07:03,360
Take it, and for a short time,

119
00:07:03,759 --> 00:07:06,480
your power will increase tenfold.

120
00:07:06,839 --> 00:07:08,040
Such a miracle drug?

121
00:07:12,439 --> 00:07:15,759
But it will cost you
twenty years of your life.

122
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:17,519
What?

123
00:07:18,279 --> 00:07:19,160
Twenty years?

124
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,279
So what?

125
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,120
Twenty years

126
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:27,879
for the Shan family head position.
Worth it.

127
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,360
Smart choice.

128
00:07:46,199 --> 00:07:47,000
Help me up.

129
00:07:49,199 --> 00:07:50,120
Shameless.

130
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:52,079
Don't!

131
00:07:52,079 --> 00:07:54,040
That traitor's already
at peak Mystic-level.

132
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,600
Su Wubing, you should go.

133
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:57,480
I'll handle this.

134
00:07:58,519 --> 00:07:59,920
None of you are leaving.

135
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:02,120
Today, you all die here.

136
00:08:31,481 --> 00:08:35,584
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

137
00:08:35,584 --> 00:08:40,304
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

138
00:08:40,304 --> 00:08:45,184
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

139
00:08:45,184 --> 00:08:50,304
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

140
00:08:50,304 --> 00:08:54,704
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

141
00:08:54,704 --> 00:08:59,384
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

142
00:08:59,384 --> 00:09:04,784
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

143
00:09:04,784 --> 00:09:11,178
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪
